name: Internet Age
overview:
Internet Age is an online publishing company from Poland, known mainly for social and classifieds websites about pets and other animals. The company was established in 2006 with its first website: Psy.elk.pl - information and social portal about dogs. Soon other websites followed: Koty.org.pl - similar portal about cats and Morusek.pl - very successful classifieds website about animals.

In 2009 Internet Age started expanding to other branches. First was tourism with travel portal ZaMiasto.com.pl, and another classifieds website: CiekaweMiejsca.org. In 2010 the company expanded to construction industry with Budowlanki.pl - website with offers of construction companies and SpytajFachowca.pl - question & answer website.

All websites owned by Internet Age have in total more than 800 000 visits and more than 6 000 000 pageviews monthly.
